Ele:
* Save the current Editor state (file buffers, edit views) every second.
  --restore will auto-open them.

* Every draw(), store the edit l,c in buffer l,c. When opening a buffer, go to
  this l,c immediately.

  * Buf is just {path, l,c}. The edits will just be {{split=, path=, l,c}.  Tmp
  * or game buffers will be ignored.

